'''瑞典西方航空294号班机'''是一班从[[奥斯陆|奥斯陆]]飞往[[特罗姆瑟|特罗姆瑟]]的货运班机。2016年1月8日，执飞该次航班的庞巴迪[[龐巴迪CRJ|CRJ200]]飞机在飞行途中坠毁。起飞大约30分钟后，该航班发布[[Mayday|Mayday]]求助信号，随后这架飞机与地面失去联絡。失事地点有一个一个火山口状的大坑，四周的雪原上散布着残骸。现场情况显示该机几乎是垂直撞击地面的。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://avherald.com/h?article=4920a18a&opt=0|title=Crash: West Atlantic Sweden CRJ2 near Akkajaure on Jan 8th 2016, lost height after emergency call|accessdate=2016-01-08|publisher=Aviation Herald|website=AvHerald|archive-date=2016-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160208131625/http://avherald.com/h?article=4920a18a&opt=0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.thelocal.no/20160108/norwegian-plane-crashes-in-swedish-mountains|title=Swedish firm 'sorrow' over Nordic plane crash|date=2016-01-08|publisher=Thelocal.no|access-date=2016-03-05|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108235627/http://www.thelocal.no/20160108/norwegian-plane-crashes-in-swedish-mountains|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 飞行经过 ==
当地时间23:11分，瑞典西方航空294号班机从[[奥斯陆加勒穆恩机场|奥斯陆加勒穆恩机场]]起飞飞往特罗瑟姆。该机共装有4.5吨的航空邮件。大约23:31，当该机在33000英尺的高度巡航时，飞行员突然宣布Mayday，随后这架飞机在雷达上消失。<ref>{{Cite tweet|author=Flightradar24|author-link=Flightradar24|user=flightradar24|number=685358745111638016|date=2016-01-08|title=ModeS data from flight #PT294 shows that it was falling very fast – from 33,000 to 11,725 feet {{bracket|{{convert|33000|to|11725|ft|disp=out}}}} in 60 seconds t.co/f3Z8Gy10O5|archive-url=https://timetravel.mementoweb.org/memento/20160110195041/twitter.com/flightradar24/status/685358745111638016|archive-date=2016-01-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 搜救 ==
挪威和瑞典方面都参与了搜救行动。凌晨3:10分，他们发现了残骸。坠毁地点位于海拔约1000米的瑞典[[阿卡湖|阿卡湖]]附近的偏远地区，距离挪威边界10千米左右。<ref name="Hradecky2016">{{Cite web|url=http://avherald.com/h?article=4920a18a|title=Crash: West Atlantic Sweden CRJ2 near Akkajaure on Jan 8th 2016, lost height after emergency call|date=2016-01-26|last=Hradecky|first=Simon|work=The Aviation Herald|dead-url=no|accessdate=2016-03-05|archive-date=2017-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305090421/http://avherald.com/h?article=4920a18a}}</ref>
飞机残骸散布在方圆大约50米内的区域，这显示飞机触地时速度極快<ref name="Hradecky2016"/>

== 涉事飞机 ==
涉事飞机于1993年出厂并交由汉莎航空运营。2006年，该机被改装为CRJ200PF货机。2007年这家飞机交由瑞典西方航空运营，注册号改为SE-DUX。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.planespotters.net/airframe/Canadair/CRJ-100-Series/7010/SE-DUX-West-Air-Sweden|title=SE‑DUX West Air Sweden Canadair CL‑600‑2B19 Regional Jet CRJ‑200PF — cn 7010|accessdate=2016-01-08|website=www.planespotters.net|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304052954/https://www.planespotters.net/airframe/Canadair/CRJ-100-Series/7010/SE-DUX-West-Air-Sweden|dead-url=no}}</ref>飞机失事时，飞机已经执行超过31000次航班，总飞行时数达到38000小时。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://aviationtribune.com/safety/item/3130-west-atlantic-crj200pf-crashes-in-sweden |title=West Atlantic's CRJ200PF crashes in Sweden |accessdate=2016-01-08 |website=aviationtribune.com |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20160109083452/http://aviationtribune.com/safety/item/3130-west-atlantic-crj200pf-crashes-in-sweden |archivedate=2016-01-09 }}</ref>

执飞当次航班的42岁的西班牙籍机长有3200小时经验。法籍副驾驶也有3050小时的经验。

== 调查 ==
瑞典事故调查局（{{lang|sv|Statens Haverikommission}}，简称SHK）已经展开对本次事故调查。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.havkom.se/en/news/2016/flygolycka-i-de-svenska-fjaellen|title=Aircraft accident in the Swedish mountains|accessdate=2016-01-09|website=www.havkom.se|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304113934/http://www.havkom.se/en/news/2016/flygolycka-i-de-svenska-fjaellen|archivedate=2016-03-04}}</ref>2016年1月9日，调查人员发现了已经严重受损的飞行数据记录仪和座舱语音记录仪。然而，内部的存储设备已经丢失。不过第二天，调查人员还是在人体残骸边发现了遗失的部件。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.havkom.se/en/investigations/civil-luftfart/olycka-i-lappland-med-flygplanet-se-dux-av-typen-canadair-crj-200|title=Accident in the arctic north of Sweden to a Canadair CRJ 200 aircraft (SE-DUX)|accessdate=2016-01-10|archive-date=2018-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180609074218/https://www.havkom.se/en/investigations/civil-luftfart/olycka-i-lappland-med-flygplanet-se-dux-av-typen-canadair-crj-200|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://polisen.se/Aktuellt/Pressmeddelanden/Norrbotten/xx/|title=Fynd vid flygplansvraket, Akkajaure|accessdate=2016-01-14|archive-date=2016-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160125220929/https://polisen.se/Aktuellt/Pressmeddelanden/Norrbotten/xx/|dead-url=no}}</ref>1月12日,瑞典事故调查局声称事故发生前飞行员仅是重复了几次"MayDay"，没有说明其他情况。1月26日，调查人员声称他们已经获得CVR和FDR数据，正在进行进一步分析和确认。<ref name="Hradecky2016"/>FDR数据显示，飞机撞击地面时速度为508节，远高于CRJ200飞机可以承受的最高速度315节。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Interim Report released on 9 March, 2016.|url=http://www.havkom.se/assets/reports/SRL-2016_01e.pdf|website=www.havkom.se|accessdate=2016-03-10|archive-date=2020-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200116021017/https://www.havkom.se/assets/reports/SRL-2016_01e.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>


